 />\n廉署於本周三（7月11日）接獲入境處轉介的投訴，指稱吳涉嫌在羅湖管制站行賄一名入境處人員，該高級入境事務助理員拒絕收受賄款，並向其上司匯報有關事件。廉署人員隨即前往現場，以涉嫌觸犯有關貪污罪行將其拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n去年本港也曾發生同類案件，一名68歲內地女子被控向入境處人員提供1000元賄款，以准許她經入境處落馬洲支線管制站進入香港，其後被判入獄15個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180714/s00002/1531506612943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180714%2Fs00002%2F1531506612943&d=bJxTfcuo2CwFfVN18A5NBNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=582e0000\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180714%2Fs00002%2F1531506612943&h=c2a2dc25\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180714/s00002/1531506612943</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"68歲果個最後咪成功咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e85c5ac5a2c8b8cfaa5a06c7ca0fe0dcba8bf0","tid":741680,"uid":159234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"起碼4萬啦   400蚊跌都跌左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36680a15351f29c545426b595dddc265965d6405","tid":741680,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4cccb6c9d4433529897ae88d353de7362abb3b","tid":741680,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:44:32.000Z","msg":"海關：人仔跌緊喎，你玩野呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:06:47.000Z","msg":"入境喎，師兄"}]}